data.description: Who needs vacation, when you have your very own paradise at home!? Gradually updated in the last few years. With multiple levels and amazing spaces, this place is destined for epic entertainment and/or private oasis! Noteworthy backyard fenced for privacy, custom firepit nestled into the ground. Inground pool with transferable warranty for the liner. Poolhouse with bar, cable and TV. Relax in the livingroom with the calming sounds of a waterfall. New deck with pergola and a hanging mister to help you cool off on the hot days to come! Third car garage growling with workshop energy just waiting for its next tinker project. So much to see!
